港浸會大學聯合國際學院<br />\n<br />\n新成員：<br />\n香港科技大學深圳研究院"},{"pid":"e790cf459b80e4c583221ed1a432e6641411230d","tid":673632,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"開分校咁多經費<br />\n肥過肥仔水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e560bab61392bdd80e10bce697af8363a04fe69","tid":673632,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:14:39.000Z","msg":"中國(香港)科技大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33728e9c149f5a1d5f00f070559f7acac566d2d0","tid":673632,"uid":14299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:18:09.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99606a189612edf1598a55101277802093e46861","tid":673632,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:40:31.000Z","msg":"廣州(香港)火雞大學"},{"pid":"6595ada54f25523db0bbcc969b804725dee25162","tid":673632,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"廣州係自己友，有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cddd7fc7ad55800aebf185de9e41ea9d86a6f81","tid":673632,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6595ada54f25523db0bbcc969b804725dee25162","tid":673632,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:44:23.000Z","msg":"廣州係自己友，有乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"你的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}